byline.contributor: Andrew E. Kramer contributed reporting from Moscow.

abstract: Vice Pres Joseph R Biden Jr urges Ukrainian leaders to fulfill promise of 2014 uprising and created united, democratic Ukrainian nation.
lead_paragraph: The American vice president, addressing Parliament in Kiev, called on politicians to limit the power of business moguls and to put aside self-interest.

headline.main: In Ukraine, Joe Biden Pushes a Message of Democracy
